snippet.textDisplay: This is a step in the right direction. DLC for $30 and the ability to continue off an existing game is a FAR better deal than buying a full price re-release of a game, with minor updates. It's also EXCELLENT that more National Dex Pokemon have been added back into to the game, and for FREE, no less! This was a GOOD decision... Now let's just keep up with that decision. In 2021, I wanna see the remaining Pokemon added back into the game. I'd even buy another DLC expansion, provided you create new content for it too, to justify the efforts... The cuts to the National Dex, cutting Megas and Z moves, and the lies were all HUGE mistakes. Game Freak can work their way back from this though, through updates like this. Don't stop here! Please!
